{
  "texts": [
    "Farmers can utilize the yield prediction to make knowledgeable management and financial decisions.",
    "Performances of new hybrids can be predicted in new and untested locations (Khaki and Wang, 2019).",
    "However, successful crop yield prediction is very difficult due to many complex factors.",
    "For example, genotype and environmental factors often have interactions with each other, which makes the yield prediction more challenging.",
    "Environmental factors such as weather components often have complex nonlinear effects, which are difficult to estimate accurately."
  ]
}